author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico City with La Ciencia Simple performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded October 17, 2024.

Songs:
Ecos 00:33
Pájaros negros 05:51
Cruz del sur 11:56
Sueño azul 18:00
Magnolia 22:48

Edgar Sandoval - Guitar, Synthesizer
Gonzalo Valencia - Drums, Sequences
Rienzi Valencia - Guitar, Samplers
Jorge Schain - Bass

Live on KEXP in Mexico City is a partnership with Vive Latino celebrating its 25th anniversary with the support of Indie Rocks! Magazine. Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico.

Host: Albina Cabrera
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht

Recorded by Matt Ogaz & JC Vertti
Assistant Engineer: Sebastián Garrido
Audio Mixer & Mastered Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Vive Latino Support:
Jordi Puig
Itzel Flores

https://lacienciasimple.com
http://kexp.org
